The '''Executive Board''' was an organization consisting of the highest-ranked officials in the [[Tagge Corporation]], a wealthy and powerful company owned by the [[House of Tagge|Tagge family]]. The Board was headed by the company's head [[Lady]] [[Domina Tagge]] and convened for official meetings aboard TaggeCo's [[flagship]] ''[[Acquisitor]]''.<ref name="Boushh" />

Led by Domina, the Board consisted of seven other members. [[Orman Tagge]] was the [[Head of Manufacturing]]; [[Ulric Tagge]] served as the [[Head of Public Relations and Messaging]]; the [[Head of Finance|Heads of Finance]] were [[Adelaide Tagge|Adelaide]] and [[Felix Tagge]], who were a couple; [[Silas Tagge]] was the [[Head of Weapons Development]]; [[Layla Tagge-Faulken]] was the [[Head of Talent Acquisition]]; and the [[Imperial officer]] [[Brace Tagge-Faulken]] also served on the Board.<ref name="Boushh" />

